      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> onion wedges </strong>to one half of a baking tray (or two) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Line the other half of the baking tray[s] with <strong>baking paper</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
