          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate</p><p>Crack your<strong> egg[s]</strong> into a shallow bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Coat the <strong>chicken</strong> in the<strong> flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add it into the <strong>beaten egg</strong> and finally press it into the <strong>seeded breadcrumb mixture</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>seeded chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
