        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>seeded chicken</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s] with the onion wedges</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!), turning once halfway through</p>",
