        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> roasted onion wedges</strong>, <strong>boiled potatoes </strong>and <strong>apple</strong> <strong>matchsticks</strong> over the <strong>salad </strong>– this is your <strong>potato</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Top the potato salad with the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>seeded</strong> <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
